            "url": "https://x-17.top/2022/10/10/docker%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%89%8B%E5%86%8C/",
            "title": "docker使用手册",
            "date_published": "2022-10-10T14:08:41.000Z",
            "content_html": "<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"\\assets\\css\\APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"\\assets\\js\\APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><script class=\"meting-secondary-script-marker\" src=\"\\assets\\js\\Meting.min.js\"></script><h1 id=\"centos-docker-安装\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#centos-docker-安装\">#</a> CentOS Docker 安装</h1>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">curl -fsSL https://get.docker.com | bash -s docker --mirror Aliyun</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>设置仓库</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\">$ </span><span class=\"language-bash\">sudo yum-config-manager \\</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-bash\">    --add-repo \\</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"language-bash\">    http://mirrors.aliyun.com/docker-ce/linux/centos/docker-ce.repo</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>安装 Docker EC</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// 最新版本</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\">$ </span><span class=\"language-bash\">sudo yum install docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io docker-compose-plugin</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">// 特定版本</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\">$ </span><span class=\"language-bash\">sudo yum install docker-ce-&lt;VERSION_STRING&gt; docker-ce-cli-&lt;VERSION_STRING&gt; containerd.io</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>安装 Ubuntu</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\">$ </span><span class=\"language-bash\">docker pull ubuntu:[version]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"docker-基础命令\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#docker-基础命令\">#</a> docker 基础命令</h1>\n<p>启动 docker</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">systemctl start docker</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>关闭 docker</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">systemctl stop docker</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>重启 docker</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">systemctl restart docker</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>查看 docker 运行状态</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">systemctl status docker</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>查看 docker 版本号信息</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker version</span><br><span class=\"line\">docker info</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>docker 帮助</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker --help</span><br><span class=\"line\">docker pull --help</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"docker-镜像命令\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#docker-镜像命令\">#</a> docker 镜像命令</h1>\n<p>查看服务器中 docker 镜像列表</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\">$ </span><span class=\"language-bash\">docker images</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>搜索镜像<br>\n拉取镜像<br>\n运行镜像<br>\n删除镜像<br>\n强制删除镜像<br>\n保存镜像<br>\n加载镜像<br>\n查看镜像<br>\n镜像标签</p>\n<h1 id=\"docker-容器命令\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#docker-容器命令\">#</a> docker 容器命令</h1>\n<p>查看正在运行容器列表</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker ps</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>查看所有容器<br>\n运行容器</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\">$ </span><span class=\"language-bash\">docker run -itd --name [name] [CONTAINER:VERSION]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>进入容器</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta prompt_\">$ </span><span class=\"language-bash\">docker <span class=\"built_in\">exec</span> -it [name] /bin/bash</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>未完待续，睡了睡了</p>\n",
